    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n\\int_{1}^{2} [4f(x) - 2x] dx &= 1 \\Leftrightarrow 4\\int_{1}^{2} f(x) dx - 2\\int_{1}^{2} x dx = 1 \\Leftrightarrow 4\\int_{1}^{2} f(x) dx - 2 \\cdot \\frac{x^2}{2} \\Big|_{1}^{2} = 1 \\\\\n\\Leftrightarrow 4\\int_{1}^{2} f(x) dx &= 4 \\Leftrightarrow \\int_{1}^{2} f(x) dx = 1\n\\end{aligned}\n$$"
